HELPLET_DATE:
Fakahū ʻa e ʻahó ʻi ha taha ʻo e ngaahi founga angamahení. Hangē ko ʻení:
  • 24 Sune 1962
  • Sune 1962
  • 1962
  • 1962 nai
  • Kimuʻa ʻi he 1962
  • Hili ʻa e 1962
  • Vahaʻa ʻo e 1961 mo e 1962
Ako lahi ange kau ki hono tohi ʻo e ngaahi ʻaho angamahení.
Ako ki he meʻa ke fai ʻi he taimi ʻoku ʻikai ke ke ʻilo ai ha ʻaho paú.
HELPLET_PLACE:
Fakahū ʻa e feituʻú ʻi ha founga angamaheni. Hangē ko ʻení:
  • Lokateila, Lanikasia, ʻIngilani
  • Potou, Falanisē
  • Palāsila
Ako lahi ange fekauʻaki mo e founga pau hono tohi ʻo e ngaahi feituʻú.
Ako ki he founga ke fokotuʻu ai ha fakalahi pe fakatonutonu ki he ngaahi feituʻu angamahení.
HELPLET_STANDARDIZED_DATE:
Kapau ʻoku hala pe teʻeki ke fakafonu ʻa e ʻaho angamahení, fili ha tuʻunga angamaheni ʻe lelei taha mo e ʻaho naʻá ke fakahuú.

Ako lahi ange ki he ngaahi ʻaho angamahení.
Ako ʻa e meʻa te ke fai ʻi he taimi he ʻikai te ke ʻilo ai ha ʻaho paú.
HELPLET_STANDARDIZED_PLACE:
Kapau ʻoku hala pe teʻeki ke fakafonu ʻa e feituʻu angamahení, fili ha tuʻunga ʻe ofi taha ki he feituʻu naʻá ke fakahuú.

Ako lahi ange kau ki hono fakahū ʻo e ngaahi feituʻu angamahení.
